    "The study found positive sentiments were more prevalent in the tweets than negative sentiments.",
    "The study also revealed the diverse range of emotions held by higher education faculty regarding ChatGPT, with trust and joy being the most prevalent positive sentiments and fear and anger being the most prevalent negative sentiments.",
